    </view>
    <view class="pre-view-content">
      <text class="pre-activity-time">SEPT 13</text>
      <view class="pre-activity-view">
        <image class="pre-activity-image" mode="widthFix" src="../../resources/images/tmp/ac2.png"></image>
        <text class="pre-activity-title">中秋百家宴——悠年与你团圆过中秋</text>
        <text class="pre-activity-intro">送你一块月饼，再送你一个圆圆的月亮</text>
